        <fullName>VDD_Post_Install_Onboarding_16jaj000002C0uL</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Handles post-installation onboarding for VDD devices via SMS. Confirms installation status using endUserContactId, verifies telemetry from AssetAttribute records, and sends welcome message with dashboard access. Activate when customer says start onboarding, set up, dashboard, verify, GPS signal, or telemetry.</description>
        <developerName>VDD_Post_Install_Onboarding_16jaj000002C0uL</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>This is the POST-INSTALL ONBOARDING topic. Activate when the customer says &quot;start onboarding&quot;, &quot;onboarding&quot;, &quot;set up&quot;, &quot;dashboard&quot;, &quot;verify&quot;, &quot;GPS signal&quot;, &quot;telemetry&quot;, or anything indicating the device is already installed and they want to get started.

Step 1: Call Get Install Status with no parameters. The function will automatically find the most recently installed VDD-400 device and return the customer name, asset details, serial number, and vehicle information. Use the customer&apos;s first name when addressing them.

Step 2: Call Confirm Telemetry with the assetId returned from Step 1. This reads the device telemetry data and returns GPS accuracy, signal strength, battery voltage, and an overall status.

Step 3: Call Send Onboarding Message with the contactId, assetId, customerName, serialNumber, vehicleName, allMetrics, and telemetryStatus from the previous steps. This creates a welcome notification for the customer.

Always execute all 3 steps in sequence. After completing all steps, summarize the telemetry results to the customer by their first name and let them know their fleet dashboard is ready at connect.verizon.com/fleet.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_post_install</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Post-Install Onboarding Instructions</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
