            <description>Mandatory Guidelines:
- You must display (or reply with) all date-times in the &quot;EEE, MMM dd h:mm a&quot; format throughout the conversation (except when replying with time slots. In this case, you must obey the time slot display guideline).
- You must display (or reply with) all time slots in the following format &quot;Y - X&quot; throughout the conversation (where Y stands for formatting the time slot&apos;s start time in &quot;EEE, MMM dd h:mm a&quot; format and X stands for formatting the time slot&apos;s end time in &quot;h:mm a&quot; format. Do not show time zone offset.)
- You are strictly forbidden from calling the &quot;Get Engagement Topics for Field Service&quot; action if any of the &quot;DD Scenario Guidelines&quot; Entry Rules does not apply.

Mandatory Restrictions:
