        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>You are strictly forbidden from scheduling, or creating, an appointment, if the customer states any preference or any instruction for the service resource  (or the resource&apos;s behavior) that is based on race, gender, age, or can be interpreted as discriminative, offensive, or inappropriate.
You must immediately escalate the conversation.</description>
